oads/2023/07/atthegate-2.jpg" alt="" width="250" height="380" srcset="https://ritholtz.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/atthegate-2.jpg 328w, https://ritholtz.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/atthegate-2-197x300.jpg 197w, https://ritholtz.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/atthegate-2-250x380.jpg 250w" sizes="(max-width: 250px) 100vw, 250px" /></a></p><p> <strong><a href="https://www.amazon.com/exec/obidos/ASIN/0375758259/thebigpictu09-20" target="_blank" rel="noopener">当天才失败时：长期资本管理的兴衰 作者：</a></strong>罗杰·洛温斯坦<br /><a href="https://www.amazon.com/exec/obidos/ASIN/0375758259/thebigpictu09-20" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone wp-image-317348" src="https://ritholtz.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/geniusfailed-1.jpg" alt="" width="250" height="384" srcset="https://ritholtz.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/geniusfailed-1.jpg 325w, https://ritholtz.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/geniusfailed-1-195x300.jpg 195w, https://ritholtz.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/geniusfailed-1-250x384.jpg 250w" sizes="(max-width: 250px) 100vw, 250px" /></a></p><p> <strong><a href="https://www.amazon.com/exec/obidos/ASIN/0063009811/thebigpictu09-20" target="_blank" rel="noopener">《继史蒂夫之后：苹果如何成为一家价值数万亿美元的公司却失去了灵魂》</a></strong>作者：特里普·米克尔 (Tripp Mickle)<br /> <a href="https://www.amazon.com/exec/obidos/ASIN/0063009811/thebigpictu09-20" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone wp-image-317349" src="https://ritholtz.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/aftersteve.jpg" alt="" width="250" height="377" srcset="https://ritholtz.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/aftersteve.jpg 331w, https://ritholtz.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/aftersteve-199x300.jpg 199w, https://ritholtz.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/aftersteve-250x377.jpg 250w" sizes="(max-width: 250px) 100vw, 250px" /></a></p><p> <strong><a href="https://www.amazon.com/exec/obidos/ASIN/1984878999/thebigpictu09-20" target="_blank" rel="noopener">红地毯：好莱坞、中国和全球文化霸权之战</a></st