opener">发表明确的</a>看法零保留。</p><p>通货膨胀率在一年前达到峰值，现在同比下降至 3%，情况又如何呢？</p><p> 60% 的受访者认为通胀“持续加剧”。我的数学成绩从 9% 下降到 3% 是下降了，但是……</p><p> <a href="https://ritholtz.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/infla.jpg" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone wp-image-317426" src="https://ritholtz.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/infla.jpg" alt="" width="600" height="569" srcset="https://ritholtz.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/infla.jpg 1265w, https://ritholtz.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/infla-300x285.jpg 300w, https://ritholtz.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/infla-1024x971.jpg 1024w, https://ritholtz.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/infla-768x729.jpg 768w, https://ritholtz.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/infla-250x237.jpg 250w" sizes="(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px" /></a></p><p></p><p>正确/错误的轨道怎么样？请注意，这种情况在选举期间发生了多大变化，这意味着人们并没有告诉你他们真正相信什么，而是透露了他们的党派偏好。</p><p> <a href="https://ritholtz.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/track.png" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone wp-image-317427" src="https://ritholtz.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/track.png" alt="" width="600" height="320" srcset="https://ritholtz.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/track.png 1800w, https://ritholtz.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/track-300x160.png 300w, https://ritholtz.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/track-1024x546.png 1024w, https://ritholtz.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/track-768x410.png 768w, https://ritholtz.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/track-250x133.png 250w, https://ritholtz.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/track-1536x819.png 1536w" sizes="(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px" /></a></p><p><em>底线仍然是</em>：人们在预测未来方面确实没有太多运气，他们很容易被自己部落的成员说服，并且在理解自己的思维过程方面不太准确。问一个关于经济状况或经济状况的简单问题，结果往往是一堆矛盾的东西。</p><p>人类是自己故事的不可靠叙述者。</p><p></p><p></p><p><em>以前</em>：<br /> <a href="https://ritholtz.com/2023/05/half-empty/">“玻璃半空”投资者</a>（2023 年 5 月 8 日）</p><p><a href="https://ritholtz.com/2022/08/partisan-sentiment/">党派之争是否会影响消费者情绪？</a> （2022 年 8 月 9 日）</p><p><a h